[threecol_one]
[dropcap]W[/dropcap]hen you need to get your company design or logo out there, our custom screen printing is the answer that you’re looking for. We use plastisol inks in our custom screen printing—a true plastisol ink contains no air-polluting solvents or volatile organic compounds. This type of printing does not have a plastic heat transfer feel. It is a high quality screen print. You can rest assured that your screen printed towels are truly safe to the environment right from the start. Our screen printing lasts a long time even after repeated washing
<h2>Embroidery</h2>
<hr />
Many of the products on our website can be custom embroidered or custom screen printed. We also offer digital printing, which allows for us to print smaller runs with detail, so whether you’re looking to print one piece or 500 pieces, we can accommodate.

We can provide embroidery on most of our soft goods, the pricing and script on this page is to offer ideas of what we can provide, if you have a particular design or lettering send us an email and we will contact you with the cost for the embroidery.
[/threecol_one]
[threecol_two_last]
<h2>Have Questions?</h2>
<hr />
Each and every design is different, so we ask you to send us your design with our upload link then email us with questions and information about your project.

Not sure where to start? It’s best to use a design with large features and clear details. This will ensure that the logo or image is clear and visible. If you’re unsure about your design, we have a detailed PDF with more information please click here

If you have any questions please email or call 1-888-374-5250. A detailed information on the cost of our screen printing services can be found here.
