[threecol_one][dropcap]T[/dropcap]his is the official blog site of <a title="ACS Home and Work" href="http://www.acshomeandwork.com" target="_blank"><strong>ACS Home and Work</strong></a>. The place where we talk about anything and everything about our products, about any crafts or making a craft (be it in embroidery, quilting, sewing, screen printing, etc.), about cooking and baking, and a lot more. We will also talk about business here, from starting your own business to living with it (be it online or offline). Well, all has been said but definitely this is the place where we at ACS Home and Work and you our valued customers can have time to exchange thoughts, and opinions about certain topics. We are happy to have this blog site and hoping that we can all have some time here to share our ideas to the public.
<h2> [/threecol_one] [threecol_two_last]</h2>
<h2>The Company</h2> 
<hr />
<strong>ACS </strong>or also known as<strong> <a title="American Chair Store.com" href="http://www.americanchairstore.com" target="_blank">American Chair Store Inc.</a> </strong>is an American family owned business located in the Midwest of the United States. We are a company selling soft good products, such as flour sack towels, bathroom towels, kitchen towels, napkins, pillows, pillow cases, bathrobes, aprons, and a lot more, for wholesale or retail. We've been in the business for eight years now and still standing up to offer high quality soft good products to the public. Most of our products are American made and are 100% made in cotton. Every product orders are carefully inspected by our staffs from the time it has been purchased up to the time before it is shipped.  We guarantee you 100% satisfaction and if for any reason, you are unhappy with the product, you can return it within 30 days of receipt of your order with full refund as stated in our return policy.

The company is best known for its high quality <a title="Flour Sack Towels" href="http://www.acshomeandwork.com/Flour-Sack-Towels.html" target="_blank">Flour Sack Towels</a> which is great for embroidery and other crafts. Most of our customers are good crafters, they all have great homemade stuffs. You can check out some photos of their works in our <a href="http://facebook.com/acshomeandwork">Facebook</a> page. Aside from our good quality towels, we are also best known to our good service to our customers. We value our customers so much in a way that we make sure to only give good quality products to them with a very reasonable price and give the lowest shipping cost possible.
